mig.core

Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • mig.core.Game

  • public class Game
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class game is the principal class in the core what do this class does :
    • instentiates all Items (PhysicalObject, Key, Information)
    • instentiates all enigmas
    • instentiates all Bolt and Door linked with
    • instentiates all NPC
    • instentiates all Room
    To win the game it has to give the good killer

    • Constructor Detail

      • Game

        public Game(java.lang.String name)
        Constructor for the class Game
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the player If it is null, the player will be called "Sherlock" The player begin the aegp room The constructor will :
        • Set doors
        • Put items in rooms
        • set the killer : Babujhi
        • put NPC in room
